<inglise> Commission Regulation (EC) No 1209/2000 of 8 June 2000 determining procedures for effecting the communications prescribed under Article 41 of the Treaty establishing the European Atomic Energy Community </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (E&Uuml;) nr 1209/2000, millega m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks Euroopa Aatomienergia&uuml;henduse asutamislepingu artikliga 41 etten&auml;htud andmete edastamise kord 8. juuni 2000 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the provisions of the Treaty establishing the European Atomic Energy Community, and in particular Article 41, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Aatomienergia&uuml;henduse asutamislepingu s&auml;tteid, eriti selle artiklit 41, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the provisions of the Council Regulation (Euratom) No 2587/1999 of 2 December 1999(1), defining the investment project(s) to be communicated to the Commission in pursuance of Article 41 of the Treaty, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 2. detsembri 1999. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EURATOM) nr 2587/1999, (1) milles m&auml;&auml;ratletakse investeerimisprojektid, millest tuleb komisjonile teatada vastavalt Euroopa Aatomienergia&uuml;henduse asutamislepingu artiklile 41 </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas: </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: </eesti>
<inglise> It is the responsibility of the Commission, to the extent necessary for the fulfilment of the task devolving on it under Chapter IV of the Treaty, to determine procedure for carrying out the obligation imposed on persons and undertakings by Article 41 to communicate investment projects relating to new installations and also to replacements or conversions which fulfil the critera as to type and size laid down by the Council, </inglise>
<eesti> selles ulatuses, mis on vajalik asutamislepingu IV peat&uuml;kiga pandud &uuml;lesande t&auml;itmiseks, on komisjoni p&auml;devuses kindlaks m&auml;&auml;rata kord, mille alusel t&auml;idetakse artikli 41 kohaselt isikutele ja ettev&otilde;tetele pandud kohustust teatada uute rajatiste, samuti nende asendamise v&otilde;i &uuml;mberseadistamisega seotud investeerimisprojektidest, mis oma liigilt ja suuruselt vastavad n&otilde;ukogu s&auml;testatud kriteeriumidele, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Investment projects relating to new installations and also to replacement or conversions which fulfil the criteria as to type and size laid down by the Regulation (Euratom) No 2587/1999 shall be communicated to the Commission by means of a form, the model for which is annexed to this Regulation. </inglise>
<eesti> Uute rajatiste, samuti nende asendamise v&otilde;i &uuml;mberseadistamisega seotud investeerimisprojektidest, mis oma liigilt ja suuruselt vastavad m&auml;&auml;ruse (EURATOM) nr 2587/1999 kriteeriumidele, teatatakse komisjonile k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas esitatud vormiga. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> The obligation to communicate to the Commission the investment projects referred to in Article 41 of the Treaty devolves on persons and undertakings engaged in the industrial activities listed in Annex II to the Treaty, in respect of all installations already established or to be established within the Community; (the obligation shall, in appropriate cases, be discharged by the local management in the case of undertakings having their seat outside the Community). </inglise>
<eesti> Kohustus teatada komisjonile asutamislepingu artiklis 41 nimetatud investeerimisprojektidest h&otilde;lmab asutamislepingu II lisas loetletud t&ouml;&ouml;stusharudes tegutsevaid isikuid ja ettev&otilde;tteid ning puudutab k&otilde;iki &uuml;henduses juba olemaolevaid v&otilde;i loodavaid rajatisi (kui ettev&otilde;te asub v&auml;ljaspool &uuml;hendust, t&auml;idab vajaduse korral seda kohustust ettev&otilde;tte kohalik juhtkond). </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> Where information to be notified pursuant to article 41 of the Treaty has already been provided in the context of the submission of general data under article 37 of the Treaty, the notification can be limited to a cross reference to such previous submission and, in addition, all other information to be notified according to the content of the form which is annexed to this Regulation. </inglise>
<eesti> Kui asutamislepingu artikliga 41 etten&auml;htud andmed on juba esitatud &uuml;ldandmetes, mis tuleb esitada vastavalt asutamiselepingu artiklile 37, v&otilde;ib teatamisel piirduda viitega varasemale teatele ja lisada sellele k&otilde;ik muud andmed, mida on n&otilde;utud k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse lisas esitatud vormis. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 4 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 4 </eesti>
<inglise> Any change made in the course of carrying out investment projects communicated to the Commission in accordance with this Regulation shall be made the subject of a further communication under the same conditions. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse kohaselt komisjonile teatatud investeerimisprojektide rakendamise ajal tehtud muudatustest tuleb samu tingimusi j&auml;rgides uuesti teatada. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 5 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 5 </eesti>
<inglise> Any change made to the said form shall be published by the Commission in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&otilde;nealuse vormi muudatused avaldatakse Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 6 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 6 </eesti>
<inglise> Regulation No 1 of the Commission of the EAEC of 5 November 1958(2) is repealed with effect of the date of entry into force of the present Regulation. </inglise>
<eesti> EURATOMi komisjoni 5. novembri 1958. aasta m&auml;&auml;rus nr 1 (2) tunnistatakse kehtetuks k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse j&otilde;ustumise kuup&auml;evast. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall enter into force on the twentieth day following that of its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus j&otilde;ustub kahek&uuml;mnendal p&auml;eval p&auml;rast selle avaldamist Euroopa &Uuml;henduste Teatajas. </eesti>
<inglise> This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States. </inglise>
<eesti> K&auml;esolev m&auml;&auml;rus on tervikuna siduv ja vahetult kohaldatav k&otilde;ikides liikmesriikides. </eesti>
<inglise> Done at Brussels, 8 June 2000. </inglise>
<eesti> Br&uuml;ssel, 8. juuni 2000 </eesti>
